OL,3,CFather of seven-year-old infected
OL,4,Cblood victim wants prosecutions after
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe father of one of the infected
OL,8,Fblood scandal's youngest victims has
OL,9,Fsaid he wants to see prosecutions
OL,10,Ffollowing the inquiry, which concludes
OL,11,Ftoday (Monday, 20 May).
OL,13,FNewport couple Colin and Janet Smith's
OL,14,Fseven-year-old son, also called Colin,
OL,15,Fdied in 1990 after contracting HIV and
OL,16,Fhepatitis C from contaminated blood
OL,17,Fproducts.
