OL,7,FHe is one of around 3,000 victims to
OL,8,Fhave died and more than 30,000
OL,9,Finfected in what has widely been
OL,10,Fdescribed as the worst health scandal
OL,11,Fin UK history.
OL,13,FHis parents have been campaigning for
OL,14,Fjustice ever since, and believe the
OL,15,Finquiry's final report is "going to be
OL,16,Fa revelation to a lot of people".
OL,18,FThe pair said they have not received
OL,19,Fany compensation, despite the inquiry
OL,20,Frecommending in April 2023 that .
