OL,7,FThe UK Government is expected to
OL,8,Funveil a for those affected.
OL,10,FJanet also wants to receive an
OL,11,Fapology, saying: "I want it sincere, I
OL,12,Fwant it from the heart.
OL,14,F"Our children and all people that have
OL,15,Flost somebody, who are still fighting,
OL,16,Fstill ill, deserve a real apology and
OL,17,Fthat will go a long, long way. I just
OL,18,Fhope it's not off the cuff.
