OL,3,CFather of seven-year-old infected
OL,4,Cblood victim wants prosecutions after
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"I'm not like Jan," he said. "I don't
OL,8,Fthink the time is right for an apology
OL,9,Fnow, it's too late.
OL,11,F"They've denied and denied and denied
OL,12,Ffor nearly 40 years for some people,
OL,13,Fso an apology is just a splash in the
OL,14,Focean. I want proper compensation
OL,15,Fbecause it's the only thing left open
OL,16,Fto us."
OL,18,FColin said he would also like to see
OL,19,Fpeople prosecuted for their actions.
