OL,7,F"A few sources are saying there's a
OL,8,Fpossibility of criminal charges," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "I'm hoping that's right.
OL,11,F"I'm hoping there's a few people out
OL,12,Fthere who are sweating now because
OL,13,Fit's coming to a climax.
OL,15,F"There's a lot of anger there. I look
OL,16,Fat my other sons and their kids and
OL,17,Fthink about what he was robbed of.
