OL,7,F"I've got grandchildren, I should have
OL,8,Fmore. I should have another daughter-
OL,9,Fin-law. I should be able to go for a
OL,10,Fdrink with him. All that was taken
OL,11,Faway, and that won't be forgiven even
OL,12,Fafter this.
OL,14,F"We went to so many funerals that we
OL,15,Fstopped going, it was just dragging us
OL,16,Fdown. So many people you get to know
OL,17,Fand then all of a sudden they're not
OL,18,Fthere."
