OL,7,FJanet said: "It has been our life and
OL,8,Fit's going to change, and I'm scared
OL,9,Fof the change I suppose, because I
OL,10,Fdon't know what it's going to be like.
OL,11,FI don't know what it's going to be
OL,12,Flike not fighting for Colin if it all
OL,13,Fgets settled.
OL,15,F"If we get the results that we're
OL,16,Fexpecting on Monday, it'd be lovely to
OL,17,Ftake a deep breath, sit back, look at
OL,18,FColin's pictures and say 'we can enjoy
OL,19,Fyou now', because it's been fight,
OL,20,Ffight, fight, fight. I want to enjoy
OL,21,Fmy memories."
