OL,7,FColin said: "(He lived a) short seven
OL,8,Fyears but the pleasure he actually
OL,9,Fbrought into our life, even though he
OL,10,Fwas seriously ill most of the time, it
OL,11,Fdidn't kill his sense of humour.
OL,13,F"He'd charge us #10 a mouthful for
OL,14,Ffood when he couldn't eat, and then
OL,15,Fhe'd get to #40 or #50 and say 'go and
OL,16,Fget me a box of Lego'. His hospital
OL,17,Froom was actually cram-packed with
OL,18,FLego."
OL,20,FJanet added: "It'd be lovely to
OL,21,Freminisce instead of fighting."
