OL,7,FThe Smiths have previously revealed
OL,8,Fhow the words "Aids dead" were painted
OL,9,Fon the side of their house in huge
OL,10,Fletters, and scratched into Colin's
OL,11,Fcar.
OL,13,FThey plan to spend any compensation
OL,14,Fthey receive on their other children
OL,15,Fand grandchildren, who alongside their
OL,16,Fbrother and parents were ostracised by
OL,17,Fthe community.
OL,19,F"That to me is from little Colin, it's
OL,20,Fnot from us," Janet said.
