OL,7,F"That's what Colin would want. They
OL,8,Fsuffered too, they were known as the
OL,9,F'Aids kids'."
OL,11,FColin added: "I'd like for the boys
OL,12,Fthat are surviving to be able to just
OL,13,Fgo away and live their life in peace,
OL,14,Frather than constantly having to fight
OL,15,Fand fight and fight.
OL,17,F"It's bad enough infecting them, but
OL,18,Fto make them fight for 40 years for
OL,19,Fjustice, that's cruel, just plain
OL,20,Fcruel.
