OL,7,F"We're bad enough, we've had to sit
OL,8,Fand watch our son die. But these lads
OL,9,Fhave had to live with the consequences
OL,10,Fof what's happened, and some of them
OL,11,Fgot horrific illnesses and they're
OL,12,Fstill up and fighting. They deserve to
OL,13,Fwin and they're going to."
